    "tag": "HF",
    "text": "At that time, he was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] '39-- he was 54, 56. This is a picture of my mother, Salomea Frenkiel Slomnicki taken in the Warsaw Ghetto in 1941. My mother was born on May the 5th, 1888, in Warsaw, Poland. And was [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] taken from during the deportation of Warsaw Ghetto to-- most likely to Treblinka. I don't have any information on the date of her death.",
